"f9786c5b6a9ae8d0ae183bf268a2f3d17ea91511","tid":2029013,"uid":84646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a3041cad25a118dc92a99e92c1ec92a12c6a8e5","tid":2029013,"uid":316927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"退返啲考試費<br />\n一係重考"},{"pid":"6f097e1ccbc5629495c243865cdaa09c0d6a0927","tid":2029013,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"消息：考評局委員會決定取消文憑試歷史科爭議試題<br />\n2020-05-22 HKT 13:32<br />\n<br />\n消息指，考評局委員會就文憑試歷史科受爭議試題有決定。據了解，經開會後，委員會決定取消有關題目，有關試題佔全卷8分，考評局將交代取消試題後的後續安排。<br />\n<br />\n受爭議的歷史科必答題，要求考生評論「1900-45年間，日本為中國帶來的利多於弊」，事件引起爭議，教育局局長楊潤雄曾提出取消有關題目，特首林鄭月娥日前亦開腔回應，形容事件是「專業失誤」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527709-20200522.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527709-20200522.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BStVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=2f72d8cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527709-20200522.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4cfc435a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527709-20200522.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7c3a837055a777c664bb50e06b97f81eb8daa2f3","tid":2029013,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"組團JR<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還我作答時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf1b0dc49944c1a87a1046e66f8ca60bb9735ab","tid":2029013,"uid":26266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"係咪有學生會司法覆核<img src=\"/assets/faces/do